<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Heylman, als ir nehst gemüwet
                                <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> seit <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        eins <expan>gütl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> steens <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>czwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> edeln <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Hanaw, und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>, das nu
                        auf <app><note><q type="date">sant Michels tag</q>29.09.1411</note></app> awsgeet, also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        es umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen tün und
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>darunt<ex>er</ex></expan> etc. Als etc. und das
                            <expan>u<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
